arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convPathBlocked, idActor)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convPathBlocked)
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_Villager_CannedScream, npc_villager)
end

szUserFunctionsScript:
local function EnableLinkedActors(sGroupName)
	tMobs = Hydra.ActorsInGroup(sGroupName)
	
	for i, idLinkedActor in pairs(tMobs) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLinkedActor) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idLinkedActor) then
			Hydra.ActorSetAIBehavior(idLinkedActor, Hydra.AIBEHAVIOR_TYPE_NORMAL)
		end
	end
end
